  "description": "<p><strong>微软周三早上发表了一篇博客文章称，公司已经启动了一项名为“伴侣网络”（Companion Web）的新计划，它将帮助开发者们编写出能够在任何尺寸的显示屏上运行的网络应用。</strong>换句话说，微软希望这套开发者工具可以让用户们能够获得将IE与移动设备整合在一起的网络体验。实际上，微软早就萌生过这样的想法。微软去年宣布了 SmartGlass项目，它可以将Xbox 360和任何安装了SmartGlass应用的智能手机或平板电脑上的内容统一起来。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eceafc9/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245081.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%A3%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92+%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88IE%E4%B8%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245081.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%A3%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92+%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88IE%E4%B8%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245081.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%A3%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92+%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88IE%E4%B8%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245081.htm&amp;t=%E5%BE%AE%E8%BD%AF%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BC%B4%E4%BE%A3%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92+%E6%95%B4%E5%90%88IE%E4%B8%8E%E7%A7%BB%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%93%E9%AA%8C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share