  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/245083.htm", 
  "description": "<p><strong>市场研究公司Frost &#38;Sullivan的最新报告显示，2012年，苹果公司的Apple TV占据美国流媒体视频机顶盒市场56%的份额。Roku位居第二，份额为21%。</strong>该报告认为，AirPlay是Apple TV胜出的主要原因，这项功能简化了从笔记本和平板电脑投射到电视屏幕上的流程。Frost &#38;Sullivan表示，虽然Apple TV的内容范围相对较窄，但真正吸引用户购买的并非流媒体内容，而是Airplay功能。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eced90e/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245083.htm&amp;t=Apple+TV%E5%8D%A0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA56%25%E4%BB%BD%E9%A2%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245083.htm&amp;t=Apple+TV%E5%8D%A0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA56%25%E4%BB%BD%E9%A2%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245083.htm&amp;t=Apple+TV%E5%8D%A0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA56%25%E4%BB%BD%E9%A2%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245083.htm&amp;t=Apple+TV%E5%8D%A0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA56%25%E4%BB%BD%E9%A2%9D\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245083.htm&amp;t=Apple+TV%E5%8D%A0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E6%9C%BA%E9%A1%B6%E7%9B%92%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA56%25%E4%BB%BD%E9